ee:variables.ee:set-variable:
%dw 2.0 output application/json
var folder = (vars.documentTypeC) var filename = payload.parts.file.headers."Content-Disposition".filename --- (folder) ++ (filename)

ee:message.ee:set-payload: %dw 2.0 output application/json --- { errMsg: error.errorMessage, errDesc: error.description, errType: error.errorType.asString }
